### User Stories

1. **As a user, I want to register an account so that I can log in and place orders.**
2. **As a user, I want to log in securely so that my personal information is protected.**
3. **As a user, I want to browse food items by category so that I can easily find what I want to order.**
4. **As a user, I want to view detailed information about each food item so that I can make informed choices.**
5. **As a user, I want to add items to my cart so that I can place an order.**
6. **As a user, I want to review my cart before placing an order so that I can make any necessary changes.**
7. **As a user, I want to place an order and receive a confirmation so that I know my order has been received.**
8. **As a user, I want to provide feedback on items so that I can share my preferences.**
9. **As a user, I want to receive personalized recommendations based on my feedback so that I can discover new items I might like.**
10. **As a user, I want to contact customer support if I have any issues or questions so that I can get help.**
11. **As a user, I want to log out securely so that my account remains protected.**
12. **As a user, I want to reset my password if I forget it so that I can regain access to my account.**
13. **As a user, I want to update my profile information so that my account details are current.**
14. **As a user, I want to view my order history so that I can reorder my favorite items.**
15. **As a user, I want to receive notifications about my order status so that I know when my food will arrive.**
16. **As a user, I want to apply discount codes to my order so that I can save money.**
17. **As a user, I want to rate my overall experience so that I can provide feedback to the restaurant.**
18. **As a user, I want to browse the menu on my mobile device so that I can order food on the go.**
19. **As a user, I want to filter items by dietary preferences (e.g., vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free) so that I can find suitable options.**
20. **As a user, I want to save my favorite items so that I can quickly add them to my cart in the future.**

These user stories cover a wide range of functionalities and help ensure that the application meets the needs of its users. If you need further assistance or have any other questions, feel free to ask!
